            <div type="transcript" id="P96-149">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>If tolling bell I ask the cause.</l>
                    <l>'A soul has gone to God,'</l>
                    <l>I'm answered in a lonesome tone;</l>
                    <l>Is heaven then so sad?</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>That bells should joyful ring to tell</l>
                    <l>A soul had gone to heaven,</l>
                    <l>Would seem to me the proper way</l>
                    <l>A good news should be given.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
